# TaskFlow - Team Collaboration & Project Management Platform

A modern, real-time project management tool built with the MERN stack.

## Features
- Real-time collaboration
- Task management with Kanban boards
- Time tracking
- Team workspaces
- File attachments
- Notifications

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React, Chakra UI, Socket.IO Client
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express, Socket.IO
- **Database**: MongoDB
- **Authentication**: JWT

